'''Thabo Andrew Rametsi II''' (yavutse 17 Nyakanga 1988), azwi nka '''Thabo Rametsi,''' ni umukinnyi wa firime na producer muri  [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri serial zizwi cyane''The Giver'', ''The Gamechangers'' and ''Kalushi: The Story of Solomon Mahlangu''<ref name="tvsa">https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=17622</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 17 Nyakanga 1988 i Umlazi, KwaZulu-Natal, Afurika y'Epfo.  Nyuma yaje kwimukira muri Kempton Park yiga mu ishuri ribanza rya Norkem Park nyuma yiga mu ishuri ryisumbuye rya Norkem. Mu gihe cy’ishuri, yateje imbere ubuhanga bwe bwo gukina, anakina amatangazo yamamaza kuri tereviziyo. <ref name="kemptonexpress">https://kemptonexpress.co.za/297179/thabo-rametsi-talks-about-life-as-an-actor/</ref> Nyuma yaje kurangiza impamyabumenyi ihanitse muri UNISA. <ref name="afternoon">https://afternoonexpress.co.za/guests/thabo-andrew-rametsi/2839</ref>

Muri Mutarama 2019, ngo yaba yarahohotewe n'itsinda ry'abanyamuryango ba Johannesburg's Community Policing Forum (CPF). <ref>https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/entertainment/2019-01-09-kalushi-actor-thabo-rametsi-beaten-up-in-joburg-cbd/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2010, yakoze ibihuje gukinira na SABC1 gukina amarushanwa series ''ishuri Act.'' Hanyuma muri 2011, yakinnye nka 'David' muri serivise ya ''Wild at Heart'' . Mu mwaka wa 2012, yatangiye gukina sinema na ''Lobola ya Fanie Fourie'' akina 'Motlatsi. Yagaragaye kandi kuri televiziyo nka ''High Rollers'' nk'impfubyi 'Muzi Khuzwayo' mu 2013.  

Muri 2014, yagize uruhare mu bashyitsi mu kiganiro cya televiziyo mpuzamahanga izwi cyane mu ''gihugu'' . Nyuma yaje gukina filime ya tereviziyo ''The Gamechangers'' anakina nk'umwicanyi ruharwa ' Devin Moore ' ari kumwe n'abakinnyi mpuzamahanga bazwi cyane Daniel Radcliffe na Bill Paxton .  Muri 2016, yamenyekanye cyane muri firime yerekana ''Kalushi: The Story of Solomon Mahlangu'', yari ishingiye ku nkuru y'impamo. <ref>https://www.vukuzenzele.gov.za/mahlangus-life-through-eyes-rametsi</ref> Muri iyo filime, yakinnye cyane ' Solomon Kalushi Mahlangu ', wishwe na guverinoma ya apartheid afite imyaka 23.  Muri Nzeri 2016, yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi witwaye neza kubera uru ruhare mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya BRICS mu Buhinde. <ref name="afternoon" />

Muri 2017, yakinnye nk'umunyamakuru ushinzwe iperereza 'Tebogo Ramolang' mu gihembwe cya kane cya televiziyo ''Hard Copy'' . 

